That's the most annoying part of this restaurant. Everytime, we go there this factor will make all my friends angry.

A shop without a sign or a name shown on the outside,  visible outisde is just a very plain Japanese food shop facade in the middle of Sham Shui Po on Tsing Shan Road among all the other ordinary shops.  I like such anonymity and confidence.

This shop serves Japanese seafood Don, menu is very selected and offers only 4 options of seafood don based on varieties of seafood and portion.

Seafood is of high quality.
Nice soup stock for the finishing of the Don.
Normal no nonsense Japanese style deco, sparkling clean.
Waitress was smart and attentive, and thoughtful. (thanks for the extra ginger at the end if you read this =) )

I was lucky to be able to walk in half hour before they closed.  I heard it is not unusual to wait for 45 minutes outside.

Cash only, no service charge.
Opens for lunch and dinner hours only.
Can easily park on the nearby quiet streets.

Very nice Japanese Restaurant, they only offer three different boxes of raw fish with rice.   One box of rice would give you three different tastes, a don, rice box; two do it yourself hand rolls and a Ochatsuke, rice with soup.  The best one is the Top Special, for only $299, outstanding price for the quality of food.  Remember they only serve a fixed number of rice boxes each night, first come first serve, no reservation, and you will only be seated when everyone in your party arrived.   Good luck to try it out.
They offer three ways to enjoy the don

result.name: 宗像屋

reviews.text:
早排去左試呢間成日有朋友講嘅宗像屋。 去之前只知道佢係食日本魚生飯。 但原來係唔止魚生飯咁簡單，係一飯三食嘅魚生飯。 

男友以為我好肚餓， 所以幫我點左個比較多魚生嘅竹丼比我。前菜係一份3片嘅魚生片， 廚師有instruction提議先食1片，其他 留番一陣另一食法。  一上枱就見到一座魚生蓉山，廚師將約9到10款魚生打蓉， 加在壽司飯上。 3味食法有手卷， 魚生飯同茶泡飯。  

整個用餐經驗幾有趣， 但又不算好好， 由於間店比較細， 只有幾張枱， 所以講野要好細聲，加上我地坐係店嘅中央， 感覺較不自然。
 
食物方面， 配搭同食法很特色幾有趣， 但其實材料新鮮程度一般， 可能係將貨就價嘅關係啦。 

去開深水埗見都冇長龍都可以考慮體驗下嘅，但唔駛專情去排隊啦

The sashimi rice serving here is good but service is average and you have to wait for all your friends and relatives to be present before you can be seated (not even 99% are there). That's the most annoying part of this restaurant. Everytime, we go there this factor will make all my friends angry.
值得一試 只有4種選擇 基本上是一樣 只是量及多一至兩樣魚生
最喜愛的日本餐廳，攪碎什錦魚生飯混有柚子，很特別。 但注意坐位只有十多個，經常要排隊。
價格在地區來說算中上，食物質素一般唔太新鮮，服務都較差，好像唔太歡迎小孩子。
